#GHAATI #AnushkaShetty #KrishJagarlamudi #NagavelliVIdyaSagar #RajeevReddy #SaiBabuJagarlamudi #UVCreations #FirstFrameEntertainments

A story of a woman who is a victim, a criminal and a legend. 

GHAATI - a raw tale from the valleys of India.

snippet.description:
Pick your own Clash On video and win in-game prizes!
____________
TIMESTAMPS

00:00 INTRO
0:41 PICK YOUR CHOICE

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Maathalle Minchu Thanda Nannavale Ee Maayavi 
Chandranne Jhumki Maadi Itkondidlu Haayagi 
Muddaada Kannigondu 
Putta Aa Kennogondu Nakshathra Thandu Kodalenu Maayavi 

Maayavi Minugu Neenu 
Munjaane Bisilu Neenu 

Saaladhiro Haadu Neenu
Bekeniso Sanje Neenu 
 
Edheya Dhunige 
Belaku Neene
Neenaadhe Neenaadhe 

Yaariradha Rastheyalli
Santhaiso Avale Gaali  
Saagaradha Baaninalli 
Kangoliso Avale Neeli 

Samayaa Nee Ninthodhe
Avala Angayyalle 
Nanoonu Sharanaadhe 
Avala Gunginalle 

Sothe Hodhe Sothe Hodhe 

Nee Modhala Koneyaa Aase 
Nanna Edhege Hidiso Bhaashe

Anuraagadhali Konebeedhiyali 
Nanagu Ninagu Mane Maadiruve 
Olage Baralu Thada Inneke 
Kitakeele Naa Kaadhe 

Yaaro Naa Yaro Kanasalli Yaaru Iradhaga 
Nannavala Manasalli Naanage Bekitthu Jaaga
Ee Hrudhaya Mouna Aaguvaaaga 
Maathu Hege Aadali 

Huduki Hodhe Ello Dhooori 
Nine Sikka Shaayari

Sothe Hodhe Sothe Hodhe 

Nee Modhala Koneyaa Aase 
Nanna Edhege Hidiso Bhaashe

snippet.title: World's Highest Road on my new Hilux! ((Delhi to Ladakh Roadtrip)) 🇮🇳
snippet.description:
⭐️ Order Melodies of India (book) : https://melodiesofindia.com/
⭐️Join our Storytelling MasterClass for Youtube : https://monkeymagic.wtf/

Subscribe to Monkey Magic ((casual)) 
https://www.youtube.com/@UCF09HPp8qsoji3fc2gPIuoQ 
===========================================================

Baljeet ko test karne ka time aagya hai, chalo chale 🥳

Devenko :  https://www.instagram.com/devenko26/
Monkey Magic : https://www.instagram.com/monkeyxmagic/
BigBroBaljeet :  https://www.instagram.com/bigbrobaljeet/

===========================================================
📧 Email 📧 : monkeymagic@create.wtf 
===========================================================

In this video we do a roadtrip starting from New Delhi driving all the way to Demchok, LAC. We spend some two nights in Hanle, mesmerised by the stargazing experience, went to Umingla - which is world's highest motorable pass! 

About My Hilux (Baljeet) 
After almost a decade of waiting I finally have this, this what you see here is my love, is the sole reason I have worked so hard over the last years. I have had this impossible dream of driving from New Delhi to London since 2012-2014 now, but when I see 2014 I see this as an important dream. Our first car in 2013 was a second hand Maruti Suzuki Alto and to be able to reach here today has been a lot of sweat, sleepless nights and prayers!

But you see, today I'm here and this is just the start of my impossible dream. To be able to go anywhere, live anywhere. To be free on the road & off road.. I shall have my freedom and this beast that you see here today is just what will give me my freedom.

Everyone, meet Baljeet, that is going to take me & you to lots and lots of far off places. Let the adventure begin!

===========================================================

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS Sporting CP 4-1 Man City | Foden, Gyorkeres hat-trick & Araujo goals
snippet.description:
City suffered a night of Champions League disappointment, losing out 4-1 at Sporting CP with Viktor Gyokeres hitting a hat-trick for the hosts.

Pep Guardiola’s side had got off to a flying start in Lisbon going ahead thanks to a fourth minute goal from Phil Foden.

The Blues – who handed teenage defender Jahmai Simpson-Pusey a full debut – dominated the first half carving out a host of other chances.

But, out of nowhere, Gyokeres struck to level affairs late in the first half before Sporting then scored twice within three minutes at the start of the second half through Maximiliano Araujo and Gyokeres, via a penalty, to seize control.

snippet.description:

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 11 Teaser - 7th November 2024 - Har Pal Geo

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Haseeb Hasan
Writer: Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar

Cast:

Wahaj Ali as Bilal Abdullah 
Maya Ali as Sadaf
Usama Khan as Ammar
Hira Mani as Hamsha
Amar Khan as Dania
Saba Hameed as Farzana
Syed Mohammed Ahmed as Namdaar
Shahvir Kadwani as Zaviyaar

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Sharda Sinha Death: 'Bihar Kokila' Synonymous With Chhath Songs Passes Away During Festival At 72
snippet.description:
Sharda Sinha Death: 'Bihar Kokila' Synonymous With Chhath Songs Passes Away During Festival At 72

Renowned Bihari singer Sharda Sinha, known as the 'Bihar Kokila,' passes away at 72. Sinha was in critical condition on ventilator support after her hospitalization. Her health declined shortly after the death of her husband, Brajkishore Sinha, in September. Sharda's son Anshuman confirms her passing, mourning both a beloved mother and an iconic artist. Known for traditional wedding and Chhath songs in Bhojpuri, Sinha made a lasting impact on the music scene. Her music celebrated cultural festivals, making her a cherished figure in the industry.

Dr. Imran Patel is a well-known pediatrician based in Ahmedabad, Gujarat. Known for his compassionate approach, he runs the Asian Children’s Hospital, where he treats young patients with a unique combination of medical expertise and empathy. Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about

snippet.title: Skoda Kylaq - The Perfect Skoda for India | First Look
snippet.description: The much anticipated Skoda Kylaq - the sub-4 metre compact SUV - finally made its debut in India today. Interestingly the company also revealed the introductory price of its base trim. It’s priced at Rs 7.89 lacs (ex-showroom), thus making it the most affordable car from the brand. Based on the same MQB A0-IN platform, the Kushaq features the same 1.0L TSI (113bhp, 178Nm) that also powers the Slavia and Kushaq. Much like its siblings, this too will be made available with both 6-speed AT and 6-speed MT. To offer better ride quality, Skoda has also reworked on its suspension compared to the Kushaq. It’s 3995mm in length, and has a wheelbase of 2556mm and ground clearance of 189mm.

snippet.title: कैसे गिर गए Jetha, Sodhi और Popatlal? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Jo Jetha Wahi Sikander
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Jethalal and Sodhi got into a fight because they wanted to return Babita's scarf first. However, Popatlala enters their mess and destroys their focus. In front of Babita and the other members of the society, Jethalal and Iyer appear to grab the scarf from one another in order to announce themselves the winners. Will Babita and the members of the society have decided who will win between Iyer and Jethalal?

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1587
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the episodes of 'Jo Jetha Wahi Sikander' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTWbYoG3SaD_hKNC0g53ugi

snippet.title: ക്രിസും ദിവ്യയും വൈറൽ കല്യാണവും കമന്റടി രോഗവും  | DIVYA SREEDHAR & KRISS VENUGOPAL COUPLE INTERVIEW
snippet.description:
ക്രിസും ദിവ്യയും വൈറൽ കല്യാണവും | DIVYA SREEDHAR & KRISS VENUGOPAL | COUPLE INTERVIEW | kairalitv 

ജീവിതത്തിൽ രണ്ടുപേരും  അനുഭവിച്ചത് ഒറ്റപ്പെടൽ ആണ് |
കുളമ്പ് രോഗം പോലെ കമന്റടി രോഗം ഉണ്ട് | അതിരുകൾ ഇല്ലാത്ത സന്തോഷം എന്നത് കുടുംബാംഗങ്ങൾ ഒരുമിച്ചു എന്നതാണ് | മുൻപുണ്ടായിരുന്ന ബന്ധം ടോക്സിക് എന്ന് ഞാൻ പറയില്ല ;പക്ഷെ ഒരുമിച്ചു പോകാൻ പറ്റിയില്ല

                                                                                                                                                                                                   TV actors Divya Sreedhar and Kris Venugopal, who recently tied the knot on October 30, 2024, they have become the latest victims of cyber trolls who abused them for their age difference. .

Both are tv actors , Divya is famous for her negative roles in Malayalam and Tamil serials,  Kris is familiar grandfather in Patharamattu. They met on the set of Patharamattu and became friends, and with some help from Kris’s relative, their friendship turned into love.                                                                                             Kris proposed to Divya, and she happily accepted. They had a small, traditional wedding ceremony at Guruvayur Temple with close family and friends.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

Today, you'll find many toothpaste brands in the market claiming that they can whiten your teeth in just 2-3 days. For example, toothpastes promising shiny white teeth in just 3 days. Then there are creative products like this Whitening Kit, which claims to whiten your teeth in 7 days with fancy blue LEDs, or these whitening pens, that promise to instantly whiten your teeth. But are all these claims true, or are they just gimmicks? On the other hand, many dentists claim that we don’t even need toothpaste; we can keep our mouths germ-free and clean with just water and a brush. So, who’s right and who’s wrong? Today, we’re going to understand the fundamental science behind teeth whitening and yellowing so that after watching this video, you’ll be able to develop habits and routines that make your teeth visibly whiter. Let’s make a goal today to improve at least 2 lakh smiles, and let’s start this video with a like!

snippet.title: Reliving BeerBiceps Childhood Memories In Wadala | Tere Gully Mein Ep 87 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Be The First To Watch All Videos. Download the CurlyTales App: https://curlytale.page.link/DwNd

Join us on a nostalgic ride through the streets of Wadala with none other than Ranveer Allahbadia, AKA Beer Biceps! 

In this special episode of Tere Gully Mein, hosted by Kamiya Jani on CurlyTales, we explore the vibrant neighborhood of DaWaMa (Dadar, Wadala, Matunga), where Ranveer grew up before moving to Versova.

We dive into Ranveer’s childhood memories, from the places he loved to snack at (and gain a little weight!) like Brij Albela for samosas, chaat, and gulab jamun, to the legendary Café Mysore, a favorite of both Mukesh Ambani and Ranveer himself. 

Watch as Kamiya teases him about his serious podcast topics like, life after death, Aliens, and the Yeti, bringing out a lighter side to this fitness and motivation icon.

Catch us hanging out with his Parsi friend at Café 792, where the laughs and leg-pulling never stop! 
Don’t miss the fun banter and chemistry between two of India’s favorite YouTubers and National Award winners. It’s a trip down memory lane, local flavours, and loads of laughter. 
Hit play for an unforgettable journey through Ranveer’s roots in Mumbai!

Catch us hanging out with his Parsi friend at Café 792, where the laughs and leg-pulling never stop! 
Don’t miss the fun banter and chemistry between two of India’s favorite YouTubers and National Award winners. It’s a trip down memory lane, local flavours, and loads of laughter. 
Hit play for an unforgettable journey through Ranveer’s roots in Mumbai!

About The Episode 

In this episode, Mihir is caught off guard when Adhira needs his help to retrieve an important OTP. As Mihir juggles his feelings for Poonam and his desire to impress her, Mansi steps in to assist Adhira with her gig plans. Meanwhile, PPT supports Mihir through his quest to win Poonam's heart. Tune in for a mix of friendship and ambition as they navigate these challenges!

Series Overview

"Wrong Number Reboot" kicks off with Mihir's life turning upside down when he starts receiving endless calls meant for Adhira, a rising singer who unknowingly gives out his number to her fans. With his lively friend PPT by his side, Mihir tries to manage the chaos. Meanwhile, Adhira is navigating her own world with the help of her close friend, Manasi. Things take a twist when Rohan enters the scene, bringing new challenges to their lives. To set things straight, PPT brings in the fan-favorite mastermind, Badri.

About The Episode 

In this episode, Mihir is caught off guard when Adhira needs his help to retrieve an important OTP. As Mihir juggles his feelings for Poonam and his desire to impress her, Mansi steps in to assist Adhira with her gig plans. Meanwhile, PPT supports Mihir through his quest to win Poonam's heart. Tune in for a mix of friendship and ambition as they navigate these challenges!

Series Overview

"Wrong Number Reboot" kicks off with Mihir's life turning upside down when he starts receiving endless calls meant for Adhira, a rising singer who unknowingly gives out his number to her fans. With his lively friend PPT by his side, Mihir tries to manage the chaos. Meanwhile, Adhira is navigating her own world with the help of her close friend, Manasi. Things take a twist when Rohan enters the scene, bringing new challenges to their lives. To set things straight, PPT brings in the fan-favorite mastermind, Badri.
Get ready for a fun-filled ride of comedy, romance, and unexpected surprises!

జీవనశైలి భాగస్వామి: రాబరే
రాబేర్‌తో మీ శైలిని అప్‌గ్రేడ్ చేసుకోండి!
Rawbare యొక్క అధునాతన సన్ గ్లాసెస్‌ను వెబ్‌సైట్‌లో ప్రత్యేకంగా యువత కోసం గొప్ప ధరలకు డిజైన్ చేసి చూడండి: https://rawbare.com/ 1 కొనుగోలు చేయండి 1 ఉచితంగా పొందండి - ఇప్పుడే ఈ డీల్‌ని పొందండి!

ఎపిసోడ్ గురించి 

ఈ ఎపిసోడ్‌లో, మిహిర్ ఒక ముఖ్యమైన OTPని తిరిగి పొందేందుకు అధీరాకు అతని సహాయం అవసరమైనప్పుడు పట్టుకోబడ్డాడు. మిహిర్ పూనమ్ పట్ల తన భావాలను మరియు ఆమెను ఆకట్టుకోవాలనే అతని కోరికను గారడీ చేస్తున్నప్పుడు, మాన్సీ ఆమె గిగ్ ప్లాన్‌లో అధిరకు సహాయం చేయడానికి అడుగు పెట్టింది. ఇంతలో, పూనమ్ హృదయాన్ని గెలుచుకోవాలనే తపనతో మిహిర్‌కి PPT మద్దతు ఇస్తుంది. వారు ఈ సవాళ్లను నావిగేట్ చేస్తున్నప్పుడు స్నేహం మరియు ఆశయాల కలయిక కోసం ట్యూన్ చేయండి!

సిరీస్ అవలోకనం

"రాంగ్ నంబర్ రీబూట్" మిహిర్ జీవితాన్ని తలకిందులు చేయడంతో ప్రారంభమవుతుంది, అతనికి తెలియకుండానే తన నంబర్‌ను తన అభిమానులకు ఇచ్చే వర్ధమాన గాయని అధిర కోసం ఉద్దేశించిన అంతులేని కాల్స్ స్వీకరించడం ప్రారంభించాడు. అతని ప్రక్కన ఉన్న అతని సజీవ స్నేహితుడు PPTతో, మిహిర్ గందరగోళాన్ని నిర్వహించడానికి ప్రయత్నిస్తాడు. ఇంతలో, అధిర తన సన్నిహితురాలు మానసి సహాయంతో తనదైన ప్రపంచాన్ని నావిగేట్ చేస్తోంది. రోహన్ సన్నివేశంలోకి ప్రవేశించినప్పుడు, వారి జీవితాలకు కొత్త సవాళ్లను తీసుకువచ్చినప్పుడు విషయాలు మలుపు తిరుగుతాయి. విషయాలను సరిదిద్దడానికి, PPT అభిమానులకు ఇష్టమైన సూత్రధారి బద్రీని తీసుకువస్తుంది.
కామెడీ, రొమాన్స్ మరియు ఊహించని ఆశ్చర్యకరమైన వినోదభరితమైన రైడ్ కోసం సిద్ధంగా ఉండండి!

ఎపిసోడ్ 3 నవంబర్ 12న డ్రాప్ అవుతుంది! మిస్ చేయవద్దు!

شريك نمط الحياة: Rawbare
قم بترقية أسلوبك مع Rawbare!
اطلع على نظارات Rawbare الشمسية العصرية المصممة خصيصًا للشباب بأسعار رائعة على الموقع الإلكتروني: https://rawbare.com/ اشتر 1 واحصل على 1 مجانًا - احصل على هذه الصفقة الآن!

حول الحلقة 

في هذه الحلقة، يتفاجأ ميهير عندما يحتاج Adhira إلى مساعدته لاستعادة كلمة مرور لمرة واحدة (OTP) مهمة. بينما يتلاعب ميهير بمشاعره تجاه بونام ورغبته في إثارة إعجابها، يتدخل منسي لمساعدة Adhira في خطط الحفلة الخاصة بها. في هذه الأثناء، يدعم PPT ميهير في سعيه للفوز بقلب بونام. استمتع بمزيج من الصداقة والطموح أثناء تغلبهم على هذه التحديات!

نظرة عامة على السلسلة

تبدأ أغنية "Wrong Number Reboot" مع انقلاب حياة ميهير رأسًا على عقب عندما يبدأ في تلقي مكالمات لا نهاية لها مخصصة لأديرا، وهي مغنية صاعدة تعطي رقمه لمعجبيها دون قصد. وبوجود صديقه المفعم بالحيوية "بي بي تي" بجانبه، يحاول "ميهير" إدارة الفوضى. في هذه الأثناء، تتنقل أدهيرا في عالمها الخاص بمساعدة صديقتها المقربة ماناسي. تأخذ الأمور منعطفًا مختلفًا عندما يدخل روهان المشهد، ليجلب تحديات جديدة لحياتهم. لوضع الأمور في نصابها الصحيح، تقوم PPT بإحضار العقل المدبر المفضل لدى المعجبين، البدري.
استعد لرحلة مليئة بالمرح من الكوميديا ​​والرومانسية والمفاجآت غير المتوقعة!

الحلقة 3 ستنزل في 12 نوفمبر! لا تفوت!

লাইফস্টাইল পার্টনার: Rawbare
Rawbare দিয়ে আপনার স্টাইল আপগ্রেড করুন!
Rawbare-এর ট্রেন্ডি সানগ্লাসগুলি দেখুন বিশেষ করে তরুণদের জন্য ডিজাইন করা দারুণ দামে: https://rawbare.com/ 1 কিনুন 1 বিনামূল্যে পান - এখনই এই ডিলটি নিন!

পর্ব সম্পর্কে 

এই পর্বে, যখন অধিরার একটি গুরুত্বপূর্ণ ওটিপি পুনরুদ্ধার করতে তার সাহায্যের প্রয়োজন হয় তখন মিহির সতর্ক হয়ে যায়। মিহির যখন পুনমের প্রতি তার অনুভূতি এবং তাকে প্রভাবিত করার আকাঙ্ক্ষাকে জাগিয়ে তোলে, মানসী অধীরাকে তার গিগ পরিকল্পনায় সহায়তা করার জন্য পদক্ষেপ নেয়। এদিকে, পিপিটি পুনমের মন জয় করার জন্য মিহিরকে সমর্থন করে। বন্ধুত্ব এবং উচ্চাকাঙ্ক্ষার মিশ্রণের জন্য টিউন ইন করুন যখন তারা এই চ্যালেঞ্জগুলি নেভিগেট করে!

সিরিজ ওভারভিউ

"ভুল নম্বর রিবুট" শুরু হয় মিহিরের জীবন উল্টে যায় যখন সে অধিরার জন্য অবিরাম কল পেতে শুরু করে, একজন উঠতি গায়িকা যিনি অজান্তেই তার ভক্তদের কাছে তার নম্বরটি দিয়েছিলেন। তার প্রাণবন্ত বন্ধু পিপিটি তার পাশে, মিহির বিশৃঙ্খলা পরিচালনা করার চেষ্টা করে। এদিকে, অধীরা তার ঘনিষ্ঠ বন্ধু মানসীর সাহায্যে তার নিজের জগতে নেভিগেট করছে। রোহান যখন দৃশ্যে প্রবেশ করে তখন পরিস্থিতি মোড় নেয়, তাদের জীবনে নতুন চ্যালেঞ্জ নিয়ে আসে। জিনিসগুলি সোজা করতে, PPT ভক্ত-প্রিয় মাস্টারমাইন্ড, বদ্রীকে নিয়ে আসে।
কমেডি, রোম্যান্স, এবং অপ্রত্যাশিত চমকের একটি মজাদার রাইডের জন্য প্রস্তুত হন!

পর্ব 3 ড্রপ 12ই নভেম্বর! এটা মিস করবেন না!

ഈ എപ്പിസോഡിൽ, ഒരു പ്രധാന OTP വീണ്ടെടുക്കാൻ ആധിരയുടെ സഹായം ആവശ്യമായി വരുമ്പോൾ മിഹിർ പിടിയിലാകുന്നു. പൂനത്തോടുള്ള തൻ്റെ വികാരങ്ങളും അവളെ ഇംപ്രസ് ചെയ്യാനുള്ള ആഗ്രഹവും മിഹിർ കൈകാര്യം ചെയ്യുമ്പോൾ, അവളുടെ ഗിഗ് പ്ലാനുകളിൽ ആധിരയെ സഹായിക്കാൻ മാൻസി ചുവടുവെക്കുന്നു. അതേസമയം, പൂനത്തിൻ്റെ ഹൃദയം കീഴടക്കാനുള്ള തൻ്റെ അന്വേഷണത്തിലൂടെ പിപിടി മിഹിറിനെ പിന്തുണയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഈ വെല്ലുവിളികൾ നാവിഗേറ്റ് ചെയ്യുമ്പോൾ സൗഹൃദത്തിൻ്റെയും അഭിലാഷത്തിൻ്റെയും മിശ്രണത്തിനായി ട്യൂൺ ചെയ്യുക!

പരമ്പര അവലോകനം

"റോംഗ് നമ്പർ റീബൂട്ട്" ആരംഭിക്കുന്നത് മിഹിറിൻ്റെ ജീവിതം തലകീഴായി മാറുന്നതോടെ, അറിയാതെ തൻ്റെ നമ്പർ ആരാധകർക്ക് നൽകുന്ന വളർന്നുവരുന്ന ഗായികയായ ആധിരയെ ഉദ്ദേശിച്ചുള്ള അനന്തമായ കോളുകൾ ലഭിക്കാൻ തുടങ്ങിയപ്പോൾ. അവൻ്റെ ചടുലനായ സുഹൃത്ത് പിപിടിക്കൊപ്പം, മിഹിർ കുഴപ്പങ്ങൾ നിയന്ത്രിക്കാൻ ശ്രമിക്കുന്നു. അതിനിടെ, തൻ്റെ അടുത്ത സുഹൃത്തായ മാനസിയുടെ സഹായത്തോടെ ആധിര സ്വന്തം ലോകം ചുറ്റുകയാണ്. അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിലേക്ക് പുതിയ വെല്ലുവിളികൾ കൊണ്ടുവന്ന് രോഹൻ രംഗപ്രവേശനം ചെയ്യുമ്പോൾ കാര്യങ്ങൾ ഒരു വഴിത്തിരിവാകുന്നു. കാര്യങ്ങൾ നേരെയാക്കാൻ, PPT ആരാധകരുടെ പ്രിയപ്പെട്ട സൂത്രധാരനായ ബദ്രിയെ കൊണ്ടുവരുന്നു.
കോമഡി, പ്രണയം, അപ്രതീക്ഷിത ആശ്ചര്യങ്ങൾ എന്നിവയുടെ രസകരമായ ഒരു സവാരിക്ക് തയ്യാറാകൂ!

എപ്പിസോഡ് 3 നവംബർ 12-ന്! അത് നഷ്ടപ്പെടുത്തരുത്!

කථාංගය ගැන 

මෙම කථාංගයේ දී, වැදගත් OTP එකක් ලබා ගැනීමට අධීරට ඔහුගේ උදව් අවශ්‍ය වූ විට මිහිර්ව අසුවෙනවා. මිහිර් පූනම් කෙරෙහි ඔහුගේ හැඟීම් සහ ඇයව විශ්මයට පත් කිරීමට ඇති ආශාව හසුරුවන විට, මාන්සි ඇගේ ප්‍රසංග සැලසුම්වලට අධීරාට සහාය වීමට පියවර ගනී. මේ අතර, පූනම්ගේ හදවත දිනා ගැනීමේ ගවේෂණය හරහා PPT මිහිර්ට සහාය දක්වයි. ඔවුන් මෙම අභියෝගවලට ගමන් කරන විට මිත්‍රත්වයේ සහ අභිලාෂයේ මිශ්‍රණයක් සඳහා සුසර වන්න!

මාලාවේ දළ විශ්ලේෂණය

"Wrong Number Reboot" ඇරඹෙන්නේ මිහිර්ගේ ජීවිතය උඩු යටිකුරු වීමත් සමඟින් ඔහුට නොනවත්වාම තම රසික රසිකාවියන්ට අංකය ලබා දෙන නැගී එන ගායිකාවක් වන අධීරා වෙනුවෙන් නිමක් නැති ඇමතුම් ලැබීමට පටන් ගනී. ඔහුගේ සජීවී මිතුරා PPT සමඟින්, මිහිර් අවුල් සහගත තත්ත්වය කළමනාකරණය කිරීමට උත්සාහ කරයි. මේ අතර අධීරා ඇගේ සමීපතම මිතුරිය වන මනසිගේ උදව්වෙන් ඇගේම ලෝකයක සැරිසරයි. ඔවුන්ගේ ජීවිතවලට නව අභියෝග ගෙන දෙමින් රොහාන් දර්ශන තලයට පිවිසෙන විට දේවල් පෙරළියක් ගනී. දේවල් නිවැරදි කිරීමට, PPT රසික ප්‍රියතම මහ මොළකරු බද්‍රි ගෙන එයි.
හාස්‍ය, ආදර සහ අනපේක්ෂිත විස්මයන්ගෙන් විනෝදයෙන් පිරුණු සවාරියකට සූදානම් වන්න!

Pendant ce temps, PPT soutient Mihir dans sa quête pour gagner le cœur de Poonam. Soyez à l’écoute d’un mélange d’amitié et d’ambition alors qu’ils relèvent ces défis !

Aperçu de la série

"Wrong Number Reboot" démarre avec la vie de Mihir bouleversée lorsqu'il commence à recevoir des appels sans fin destinés à Adhira, une chanteuse montante qui donne sans le savoir son numéro à ses fans. Avec son ami PPT à ses côtés, Mihir tente de gérer le chaos. Pendant ce temps, Adhira navigue dans son propre monde avec l'aide de son amie proche, Manasi. Les choses changent lorsque Rohan entre en scène, apportant de nouveaux défis à leur vie. Pour mettre les choses au clair, PPT fait appel au cerveau préféré des fans, Badri.
Préparez-vous pour une aventure amusante pleine de comédie, de romance et de surprises inattendues !

L'épisode 3 sort le 12 novembre ! Ne le manquez pas !

Rawbare ನೊಂದಿಗೆ ನಿಮ್ಮ ಶೈಲಿಯನ್ನು ಅಪ್‌ಗ್ರೇಡ್ ಮಾಡಿ!
ವೆಬ್‌ಸೈಟ್‌ನಲ್ಲಿ ವಿಶೇಷವಾಗಿ ಯುವಜನರಿಗಾಗಿ ಉತ್ತಮ ಬೆಲೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ವಿನ್ಯಾಸಗೊಳಿಸಲಾದ Rawbare ನ ಟ್ರೆಂಡಿ ಸನ್‌ಗ್ಲಾಸ್‌ಗಳನ್ನು ಪರಿಶೀಲಿಸಿ: https://rawbare.com/ 1 ಖರೀದಿಸಿ 1 ಉಚಿತ ಪಡೆಯಿರಿ - ಈಗಲೇ ಈ ಒಪ್ಪಂದವನ್ನು ಪಡೆದುಕೊಳ್ಳಿ!

ಸಂಚಿಕೆ ಬಗ್ಗೆ 

ಈ ಸಂಚಿಕೆಯಲ್ಲಿ, ಪ್ರಮುಖ OTP ಯನ್ನು ಹಿಂಪಡೆಯಲು ಅಧಿರಾ ಅವರ ಸಹಾಯದ ಅಗತ್ಯವಿರುವಾಗ ಮಿಹಿರ್ ಕಾವಲುಗಾರನನ್ನು ಹಿಡಿಯುತ್ತಾನೆ. ಮಿಹಿರ್ ಪೂನಂ ಬಗ್ಗೆ ತನ್ನ ಭಾವನೆಗಳನ್ನು ಮತ್ತು ಅವಳನ್ನು ಮೆಚ್ಚಿಸುವ ಬಯಕೆಯನ್ನು ಕಣ್ಕಟ್ಟು ಮಾಡುತ್ತಿದ್ದಂತೆ, ಮಾನ್ಸಿ ಅಧಿರಾಗೆ ತನ್ನ ಗಿಗ್ ಯೋಜನೆಗಳೊಂದಿಗೆ ಸಹಾಯ ಮಾಡಲು ಹೆಜ್ಜೆ ಹಾಕುತ್ತಾಳೆ. ಏತನ್ಮಧ್ಯೆ, ಪೂನಮ್ ಅವರ ಹೃದಯವನ್ನು ಗೆಲ್ಲುವ ಅವರ ಅನ್ವೇಷಣೆಯ ಮೂಲಕ PPT ಮಿಹಿರ್ ಅವರನ್ನು ಬೆಂಬಲಿಸುತ್ತದೆ. ಅವರು ಈ ಸವಾಲುಗಳನ್ನು ನ್ಯಾವಿಗೇಟ್ ಮಾಡುವಾಗ ಸ್ನೇಹ ಮತ್ತು ಮಹತ್ವಾಕಾಂಕ್ಷೆಯ ಮಿಶ್ರಣಕ್ಕಾಗಿ ಟ್ಯೂನ್ ಮಾಡಿ!

ಸರಣಿ ಅವಲೋಕನ

"ರಾಂಗ್ ನಂಬರ್ ರೀಬೂಟ್" ಮಿಹಿರ್‌ನ ಜೀವನವು ತಲೆಕೆಳಗಾಗುವುದರೊಂದಿಗೆ ಪ್ರಾರಂಭಗೊಳ್ಳುತ್ತದೆ, ಅವನು ಅಧಿರಾಗಾಗಿ ಉದ್ದೇಶಿಸಿರುವ ಅಂತ್ಯವಿಲ್ಲದ ಕರೆಗಳನ್ನು ಸ್ವೀಕರಿಸಲು ಪ್ರಾರಂಭಿಸಿದಾಗ, ತಿಳಿಯದೆ ತನ್ನ ಅಭಿಮಾನಿಗಳಿಗೆ ತನ್ನ ಸಂಖ್ಯೆಯನ್ನು ನೀಡುವ ಉದಯೋನ್ಮುಖ ಗಾಯಕಿ. ಅವನ ಉತ್ಸಾಹಭರಿತ ಸ್ನೇಹಿತ PPT ಅವನ ಪಕ್ಕದಲ್ಲಿ, ಮಿಹಿರ್ ಅವ್ಯವಸ್ಥೆಯನ್ನು ನಿರ್ವಹಿಸಲು ಪ್ರಯತ್ನಿಸುತ್ತಾನೆ. ಏತನ್ಮಧ್ಯೆ, ಅಧಿರಾ ತನ್ನ ಆಪ್ತ ಸ್ನೇಹಿತೆ ಮಾನಸಿಯ ಸಹಾಯದಿಂದ ತನ್ನದೇ ಆದ ಪ್ರಪಂಚವನ್ನು ನ್ಯಾವಿಗೇಟ್ ಮಾಡುತ್ತಿದ್ದಾಳೆ. ರೋಹನ್ ಅವರ ಜೀವನಕ್ಕೆ ಹೊಸ ಸವಾಲುಗಳನ್ನು ತರುವ ದೃಶ್ಯಕ್ಕೆ ಪ್ರವೇಶಿಸಿದಾಗ ವಿಷಯಗಳು ತಿರುವು ಪಡೆದುಕೊಳ್ಳುತ್ತವೆ. ವಿಷಯಗಳನ್ನು ನೇರವಾಗಿ ಹೊಂದಿಸಲು, PPT ಅಭಿಮಾನಿಗಳ ಮೆಚ್ಚಿನ ಮಾಸ್ಟರ್‌ಮೈಂಡ್, ಬದ್ರಿಯನ್ನು ತರುತ್ತದೆ.
ಹಾಸ್ಯ, ಪ್ರಣಯ, ಮತ್ತು ಅನಿರೀಕ್ಷಿತ ಆಶ್ಚರ್ಯಗಳ ಮೋಜು ತುಂಬಿದ ಸವಾರಿಗೆ ಸಿದ್ಧರಾಗಿ!

ಸಂಚಿಕೆ 3 ನವೆಂಬರ್ 12 ರಂದು ಇಳಿಯುತ್ತದೆ! ಅದನ್ನು ತಪ್ಪಿಸಿಕೊಳ್ಳಬೇಡಿ!

लाइफस्टाइल पार्टनर: रॉबेयर
रॉबेयर के साथ अपनी शैली को अपग्रेड करें!
वेबसाइट पर विशेष रूप से युवाओं के लिए डिज़ाइन किए गए रॉबेयर के ट्रेंडी धूप के चश्मे को अच्छी कीमतों पर देखें: https://rawbare.com/ 1 खरीदें 1 मुफ़्त पाएं - इस डील को अभी प्राप्त करें!

एपिसोड के बारे में 

इस एपिसोड में, मिहिर तब हैरान रह जाता है जब अधीरा को एक महत्वपूर्ण ओटीपी प्राप्त करने के लिए उसकी मदद की आवश्यकता होती है। जैसे ही मिहिर, पूनम के लिए अपनी भावनाओं और उसे प्रभावित करने की इच्छा के साथ खिलवाड़ करता है, मानसी अपनी योजनाओं में अधीरा की मदद करने के लिए आगे आती है। इस बीच, पीपीटी, पूनम का दिल जीतने की खोज में मिहिर का समर्थन करती है। जैसे ही वे इन चुनौतियों से निपटते हैं, दोस्ती और महत्वाकांक्षा के मिश्रण के लिए तैयार रहें!

शृंखला सिंहावलोकन

"रॉन्ग नंबर रीबूट" की शुरुआत मिहिर के जीवन में उथल-पुथल के साथ होती है, जब उसे अधीरा के लिए अंतहीन कॉल आने लगती हैं, जो एक उभरती हुई गायिका है, जो अनजाने में अपने प्रशंसकों को अपना नंबर दे देती है। अपने जिंदादिल दोस्त पीपीटी के साथ, मिहिर अराजकता को संभालने की कोशिश करता है। इस बीच, अधीरा अपनी करीबी दोस्त मानसी की मदद से अपनी दुनिया में घूम रही है। जब रोहन दृश्य में प्रवेश करता है तो चीजें बदल जाती हैं, और उनके जीवन में नई चुनौतियाँ आती हैं। चीजों को सीधा करने के लिए, पीपीटी प्रशंसकों के पसंदीदा मास्टरमाइंड, बद्री को लाता है।
कॉमेडी, रोमांस और अप्रत्याशित आश्चर्य से भरी मज़ेदार सवारी के लिए तैयार हो जाइए!

एपिसोड 3 12 नवंबर को आएगा! इसे मत गँवाओ!
